      <title>伊朗总统称他准备缓解与以色列的紧张关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/iran-s-president-says-he-s-prepared-to-ease-tensions-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安表示，只要伊朗看到对方做出同样程度的承诺，伊朗就准备缓和与以色列的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/iran-s-president-says-he-s-prepared-to-ease-tensions-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安将在与肖尔茨的会晤中争取 50 亿欧元的飞机交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/turkey-s-erdogan-to-press-for-eurofighter-jet-deal-in-meeting-with-scholz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明，北约两大盟国正试图改善关系，土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安正在敦促德国批准向土耳其出售欧洲台风战斗机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/turkey-s-erdogan-to-press-for-eurofighter-jet-deal-in-meeting-with-scholz</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 15:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯不断为普京的乌克兰战争提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/russia-budget-plans-show-no-let-up-in-putin-s-war-on-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯计划在2025年将国防开支维持在历史最高水平，并且由于总统普京对乌克兰的战争没有结束的迹象，未来两年国防开支只会略有下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/russia-budget-plans-show-no-let-up-in-putin-s-war-on-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 15:48:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国参议员试图阻止墨西哥接管瓦肯港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/us-senators-seek-to-deter-mexico-from-taking-over-vulcan-port</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国两党参议员提议立法，向墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔施压，要求其放弃征用阿拉巴马州 Vulcan Materials Co. 的港口和石灰石采石场的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/us-senators-seek-to-deter-mexico-from-taking-over-vulcan-port</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 14:44:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称特朗普枪击案嫌疑人可能曾跟踪前总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/suspected-trump-gunman-likely-stalked-former-president-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部在一份文件中表示，涉嫌于 9 月 15 日试图暗杀唐纳德·特朗普的男子似乎已在特朗普位于佛罗里达的高尔夫俱乐部和海湖庄园跟踪了他一个月，此举可能会引发批评，称他本可以更早被抓获。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/suspected-trump-gunman-likely-stalked-former-president-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 14:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔遭遇 60 年来最严重干旱 提前停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecuador-begins-power-cuts-early-amid-worst-drought-in-60-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于遭遇创纪录的干旱，厄瓜多尔本周原计划在夜间进行的轮流停电被提前到白天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecuador-begins-power-cuts-early-amid-worst-drought-in-60-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 14:12:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯表示将采取雄心勃勃的预算计划，以吸引英国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/rachel-reeves-promises-real-ambition-in-uk-budget-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯暗示，她的计划可能会为气候转型和其他政府优先事项注入数十亿英镑的投资，她承诺将提供一份展现“真正雄心”的英国预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/rachel-reeves-promises-real-ambition-in-uk-budget-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 11:35:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orcel 意外增持德国商业银行股份，加剧市场竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/unicredit-raises-commerzbank-stake-to-21-amid-berlin-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔（Andrea Orcel）将该行在德国商业银行（Commerzbank AG）的股份增加了一倍以上，这一重大进展可能会加剧其与德国政府的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/unicredit-raises-commerzbank-stake-to-21-amid-berlin-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 10:31:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京要求中国严厉打击反日仇恨行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/china-says-it-doesn-t-teach-hatred-of-japan-after-child-killed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本男孩在中国被刺身亡事件发生后，中日两国政府结束了最高级别的会谈，日本一名高级外交官要求中国严厉处理网络上针对该国的“不实恶意”帖子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/china-says-it-doesn-t-teach-hatred-of-japan-after-child-killed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党，冲突升级，数百人丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地政府称，以色列周一对黎巴嫩南部真主党目标发动空袭，造成 274 人死亡，双方敌对情绪不断升级，引发国际社会对爆发全面战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 06:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
